}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 "WORSHIP NOTES" - }{\plain \fs24 \f8 On Sunday, December 2, the First Sunday of Advent, we will return to Setting I of the liturgy. \softline
As part of our Advent and Christmas worship, we will also include "A Service of Lessons and Carols" on December \softline
23 at the 8:30 service as well a Carol Setting of Martin Luther's "German Mass" on December 30 at both the 8:30 \softline
& 11:00 services. Future dates for our Modern Worship services will be December 9, January 20, and February \softline
10, all at the 11:00 service.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Men's Prayer Breakfast:}{\plain \fs24 \f8  Men of the congregation are invited to join other Living Savior men for breakfast, prayer \softline
and Bible study every 2nd and 4th Saturday from 7 - 8:30am. Our new study is on Martin Luther: Gospel and Law. \softline
Questions?  Contact Paul Gross.\par
